---
title: Garlicky Shrimp Scampi with Lemon Rice Pilaf
description: Garlic and shrimp aren't the only stars of this dish. We've paired them with a lemon rice pilaf stuffed full of peas, fresh tomatoes and bright parsley. Your taste buds will be singing!
